{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After you die, Death gives you the chance to come back to the world of the living to fulfill your deepest desire. Take the chance. Get back on your feet, and claim your revenge in this stealth action-adventure game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fulfill Your Wish</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ve been brought back with a single purpose: revenge. Attack the villages ravaged by the sinister and enslaving \u201cApocalypse Bringers\u201d, who have plunged the world into chaos, and liberate them from their tyranny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stealthy Action and Multiple Tools</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your bow and arrow to eliminate enemies from a distance. You can distract foes with an arrow and attack them from behind, or wait and confront them head-on with lethal axe strikes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428990/extras/stealthAction.png?t=1735494053\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Confront the \u201cApocalypse Bringers\u201d</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Liberate villages from their control and face their bosses. Each boss has unique mechanics that will alter your gameplay. Who knows? Maybe you can even save some of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428990/extras/bossfight.png?t=1735494053\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Immersive Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the desert\u2019s stories, complete missions for upgrades, and uncover the darkest secrets, shrouded in blood and sand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428990/extras/emotion.png?t=1735494053\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Brother's Wish","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommu